author: @educostanzo
content:
Not only she did a massive concert but she also managed to scandalize Brazilian right-wing puritans with her assertive attitude towards sexuality, kissing a trans woman onstage and finishing her performance basically reclaiming the Brazilian soccer uniform and green and yellow flag for a lot of people who had distanced themselves from it.
Not a fan of her music but I really admire what she did.
